WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
If you are logged in to your user account,

00:03.200 --> 00:05.400
you can manage your user settings

00:05.600 --> 00:08.700
by hovering over your username in the navbar

00:09.000 --> 00:12.000
and clicking on the "Edit Profile" link.

00:12.200 --> 00:14.800
Here you can change your password,

00:15.000 --> 00:16.800
your default language

00:17.000 --> 00:19.500
or your email address.

00:19.800 --> 00:22.400
Changes to your password or default language

00:22.600 --> 00:24.500
will take effect immediately

00:24.800 --> 00:26.500
whereas a change to your email address

00:26.700 --> 00:28.000
will need to be verified

00:28.000 --> 00:29.800
using a verification link

00:29.800 --> 00:33.000
sent to the new email address.
